      "body" : "@pgrigor is correct here. This is the same idea I tried to implement about a year ago.\r\n\r\nThe local node won't accept the new block itself until verification completes, but it should be capable of doing the relay in realtime to reduce the overall propagation time.",
      "created_at" : "2014-08-11T21:33:21Z",
      "html_url" : "https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/4677#issuecomment-51844029",
